Title: OPE between the energy-momentum tensor and the Wilson loop in N=4

Super-Yang-Mills theoryAuthors: Takehiro Azuma, Hikaru Kawai

Comments: 38 pages, 7 figures.(v3) translated into the PTP format (v4) some

subtleties correctedJournal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 106 (2001) 255-292

We analyze the operator product expansion T_{\mu \nu}(z) W[C] in N=44-dimensional Super-Yang-Mills (SYM) theory with U(N) gauge group, and clarifythat the closed Wilson loop does not possess an anomalous dimension and thatonly the shape of the loop is changed by the conformal transformation.